<lb n="0820b10" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 537</head>
<lb n="0820b11" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說越難經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0820b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0820b13" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0820014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">居士＝清信士【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">居士＝清信士【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820014"><lem wit="【大】">居士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清信士</rdg></app>聶承遠譯</byline>
<lb n="0820b14" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0820b1401">聞如是。一時佛在波羅奈私<note n="0820015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">國賢者飛鳥聚＝園【宮】</note><app n="0820015"><lem wit="【大】">國。賢者飛鳥
<lb n="0820b15" ed="T"/>聚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">園</rdg></app>。<note n="0820016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">彼＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彼＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820016"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>時國中有四姓長者。名曰越難。大豪
<lb n="0820b16" ed="T"/><note n="0820017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">富珍奇＝貴珍琦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">富珍奇＝貴珍琦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820017"><lem wit="【大】">富珍奇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">貴珍琦</rdg></app>珠寶牛馬田宅甚眾多。難為人慳貪
<lb n="0820b17" ed="T"/>嫉&CB00107;。不信道德不喜布施。日未沒。常&CB00330;門監。
<lb n="0820b18" ed="T"/>有來乞<note n="0820018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔&CB00456;〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔&CB00456;〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820018"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00456;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>者勿得通<note n="0820019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＝之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820019"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0820b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0820b1901">難有<note n="0820020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0820020"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>子名<note n="0820021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【宮】</note><app n="0820021"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>栴檀。亦復慳貪。難後壽盡
<lb n="0820b20" ed="T"/><note n="0820022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔還〕－【宮】</note><app n="0820022"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>生其國中。為盲乞婦作子。其夫言。汝身
<lb n="0820b21" ed="T"/>有重病。今復懷軀。<note n="0820023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我＋（以）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＋（以）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820023"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我以</rdg></app>貧窮無以衣食。汝便
<lb n="0820b22" ed="T"/>自去。婦受教出門<note n="0820024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔外〕－【宮】</note><app n="0820024"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。未遠得大聚糞。便止
<lb n="0820b23" ed="T"/>其中。至九月生一子。兩目<note n="0820025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝悉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820025"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悉</rdg></app>盲。其母<note n="0820026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820026"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>乞
<lb n="0820b24" ed="T"/>食養之。至年七歲。<note n="0820027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔其〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820027"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>母言。我養汝大久。且
<lb n="0820b25" ed="T"/>自行<note n="0820028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝持【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄＝持【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820028"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">持</rdg></app>杖。取食器行乞。當自悲言。世間貧
<lb n="0820b26" ed="T"/>者最為苦惱。今我薄命生貧家。兩目復盲無
<lb n="0820b27" ed="T"/>所<note n="0820029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820029"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見者</rdg></app>。復為人所輕易。今<note n="0820030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">有乞＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有乞＝與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820030"><lem wit="【大】">有乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">與</rdg></app>我少所<note n="0820031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飲食＝飯【宮】</note><app n="0820031"><lem wit="【大】">飲
<lb n="0820b28" ed="T"/>食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">飯</rdg></app>。愈我飢者。譬如天雨。渴者得飲。兒聞母
<lb n="0820b29" ed="T"/>說如是。便行家家乞&CB00456;。復到栴檀家。其子
<pb n="0820c" id="T14.0537.0820c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0820c01" ed="T"/>適到時守門者<note n="0820032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">適＝暫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">適＝暫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820032"><lem wit="【大】">適</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">暫</rdg></app>小出。盲兒<note n="0820033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徑入＝往入【宮】</note><app n="0820033"><lem wit="【大】">徑入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">往入</rdg></app><note n="0820034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">前到＝至【三】，前至【宮】</note><note n="0820034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前到＝至【宋】【元】【明】，＝前至【宮】</note><app n="0820034"><lem wit="【大】">前到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">前至</rdg></app>中
<lb n="0820c02" ed="T"/>庭。如母教說之。時栴檀在高<note n="0820035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觀＝樓【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀＝樓【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820035"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">樓</rdg></app>上聞其<note n="0820036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">語＝言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語＝言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820036"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">言</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0820c03" ed="T"/>大<note n="0820037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怒＋（便）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怒＋（便）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820037"><lem wit="【大】">怒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">怒便</rdg></app>呼守門者問之。誰內此盲<note n="0820038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔乞〕－【宮】</note><app n="0820038"><lem wit="【大】">乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>兒者。<note n="0820039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門監大恐怖＝監門人大懅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門監大恐怖＝監門人大懅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820039"><lem wit="【大】">門
<lb n="0820c04" ed="T"/>監大恐怖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">監門人大懅</rdg></app>。即<note n="0820040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">牽＝掣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">牽＝掣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820040"><lem wit="【大】">牽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">掣</rdg></app>盲兒<note n="0820041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撲＝撥【宮】</note><app n="0820041"><lem wit="【大】">撲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">撥</rdg></app>於門外。傷其頭面。
<lb n="0820c05" ed="T"/>復<note n="0820042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">折＋（其）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">折＋（其）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820042"><lem wit="【大】">折</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">折其</rdg></app>右臂。壞其食器飯散<note n="0820043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820043"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於</rdg></app>地。身體大痛。
<lb n="0820c06" ed="T"/><note n="0820044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兒＋（&CB00054;）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兒＋（&CB00054;）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820044"><lem wit="【大】">兒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">兒&CB00054;</rdg></app>呼悲啼。其母聞之即走到兒所<note n="0820045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔言〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820045"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。何等
<lb n="0820c07" ed="T"/>弊人嬈我子者。我子尚小。<note n="0820046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兩＝其【宮】</note><app n="0820046"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">其</rdg></app>目復盲。有何
<lb n="0820c08" ed="T"/><note n="0820047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔等〕－【宮】</note><app n="0820047"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>過<note n="0820048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乃取如是＝而取之爾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃取如是＝而取之爾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820048"><lem wit="【大】">乃取如是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">而取之爾</rdg></app>。何壹感天。兒對母言。我
<lb n="0820c09" ed="T"/><note n="0820049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">到＝至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">到＝至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820049"><lem wit="【大】">到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至</rdg></app>此門中乞。有高聲人。呼多力人<note n="0820050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">牽撲傷我身＝掣撲折傷我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">牽撲傷我身＝掣撲折傷我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820050"><lem wit="【大】">牽撲傷
<lb n="0820c10" ed="T"/>我。身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">掣撲折傷我</rdg></app>體大痛如是。今且死不久。時門上有
<lb n="0820c11" ed="T"/>守神。<note n="0820051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820051"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>謂之言。汝得是痛。尚為小耳。其
<lb n="0820c12" ed="T"/>大在後。汝坐前世有財不布<note n="0820052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">施＋（今）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施＋（今）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820052"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">施今</rdg></app>故。得勤苦。
<lb n="0820c13" ed="T"/>世間富貴無有常。富貴而不布施。如無有財
<lb n="0820c14" ed="T"/>等<note n="0820053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＝耳【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝耳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820053"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耳</rdg></app>。死更苦痛<note n="0820054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乃＝迺【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝迺【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820054"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">迺</rdg></app>愁悔當復何益。<note n="0820055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">時＝如是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時＝如是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820055"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">如是</rdg></app>觀
<lb n="0820c15" ed="T"/>者甚眾多。各各自語。其聲遠聞。</p>
<lb n="0820c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0820c1601">佛時從念道覺。與諸比丘俱入城<note n="0820056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔分衛〕－【宮】</note><app n="0820056"><lem wit="【大】">分衛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0820057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛＝遙見之便【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＝遙見之便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820057"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">遙見之便</rdg></app>
<lb n="0820c17" ed="T"/>問阿難。是何等聲。<note n="0820058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00229;&CB00229;乃＝迺【宮】</note><app n="0820058"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00229;&CB00229;乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">迺</rdg></app>如是。阿難<note n="0820059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820059"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0820c18" ed="T"/>白佛。說<note n="0820060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盲＋（兒）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盲＋（兒）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820060"><lem wit="【大】">盲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">盲兒</rdg></app>子母本<note n="0820061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＝末【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事＝末【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820061"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">末</rdg></app>已。便叉手白佛。願哀
<lb n="0820c19" ed="T"/><note n="0820062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">矜＝憐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矜＝憐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820062"><lem wit="【大】">矜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">憐</rdg></app>到此兒所。佛默然不應。分衛還飯已。便
<lb n="0820c20" ed="T"/>往視之。見盲兒<note n="0820063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">創＝瘡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0820063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">創＝瘡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0820063"><lem wit="【大】">創</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">瘡</rdg></app>痛。以手摩其頭目便即
<pb n="0821a" id="T14.0537.0821a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0821a01" ed="T"/>開。<note n="0821001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔折〕－【宮】</note><app n="0821001"><lem wit="【大】">折</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>傷處即愈。因自識宿命。佛問。汝是前
<lb n="0821a02" ed="T"/>世長者字<note n="0821002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（越）＋難【三】【宮】</note><note n="0821002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（越）＋難【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0821002"><lem wit="【大】">難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">越難</rdg></app>不。對言。是也。</p>
<lb n="0821a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0821a0301">佛告阿難。人居世間甚<note n="0821003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔懃苦〕－【宮】</note><app n="0821003"><lem wit="【大】">懃苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>愚癡。一世父
<lb n="0821a04" ed="T"/>子不相識知。</p>
<lb n="0821a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0821a0501"><note n="0821004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（爾時…意）九字＝佛故說偈言【三】，佛便說偈言【宮】</note><note n="0821004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（爾時…意）九字＝佛故說偈言【宋】【元】【明】，＝佛便說偈言【宮】</note><app word-count="9" n="0821004"><lem wit="【大】">爾時佛說經。解散其意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">佛故說偈言</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">佛便說偈言</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0821a06" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0821a0601"><note n="0821005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（人求…果）四句二十字∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note><app n="0821005"><lem wit="【大】"><l>人求子索財</l><l>於此二事中</l>
<lb n="0821a07" ed="T"/><l>甚憂勤苦痛</l><l>他人而得果</l></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">有身不能保何況子與財譬如夏月暑息止樹下涼須臾當復去世間無有常</rdg></app>
<lb n="0821a08" ed="T"/><note n="0821006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（人求…果）四句二十字∞（有身…常）六句三十字【宮】</note><app n="0821006"><lem wit="【大】"><l>有身不能保</l><l>何況子與財</l>
<lb n="0821a09" ed="T"/><l>譬如夏月<note n="0821007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">暑＝熱【宮】</note><app n="0821007"><lem wit="【大】">暑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">熱</rdg></app></l><l>息止樹下涼</l>
<lb n="0821a10" ed="T"/><l>須臾當復去</l><l>世間無有常</l></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">人求子索財於此二事中甚憂勤苦痛他人而得果</rdg></app></lg>
<lb n="0821a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0821a1101">阿難白佛。此兒命盡當趣何道。佛言。當入大
<lb n="0821a12" ed="T"/>泥梨中一宿佛說是<note n="0821008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【宮】</note><app n="0821008"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>時。八萬餘人皆棄三
<lb n="0821a13" ed="T"/>垢得法眼。諸弟子皆歡喜。為佛作禮而去。</p></div1>
<lb n="0821a14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說越難經</jhead></juan>
